The paper deals with spectrum sensing in cognitive radio networks, which involves signal processing, information theory, and communication networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
